function parseDate(s, ignoreTimezone) { // ignoreTimezone defaults to true


      

      
    
      
      

        1378
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
        if (typeof s == 'object') { // already a Date object


      

      
    
      
      

        1379
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin

        1380
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
        }


      

      
    
      
      

        1381
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
        if (typeof s == 'number') { // a UNIX timestamp


      

      
    
      
      

        1382
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                return new Date(s * 1000);


      

      
    
      
      

        1383
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
        }


      

      
    
      
      

        1384
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
        if (typeof s == 'string') {


      

      
    
      
      

        1385
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                if (s.match(/^\d+(\.\d+)?$/)) { // a UNIX timestamp


      

      
    
      
      

        1386
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                        return new Date(parseFloat(s) * 1000);


      

      
    
      
      

        1387
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                }


      

      
    
      
      

        1388
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin

        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin

        1390

        Redmine Admin

        1391
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin

        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin

        1393

function parseTime(s) { // returns minutes since start of day


      

      
    
      
      

        1453
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
        if (typeof s == 'number') { // an hour


      

      
    
      
      

        1454
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                return s * 60;


      

      
    
      
      

        1455
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
        }


      

      
    
      
      

        1456
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
        if (typeof s == 'object') { // a Date object


      

      
    
      
      

        1457
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                return s.getHours() * 60 + s.getMinutes();


      

      
    
      
      

        1458
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
        }


      

      
    
      
      

        1459
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
        var m = s.match(/(\d+)(?::(\d+))?\s*(\w+)?/);


      

      
    
      
      

        1460
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
        if (m) {


      

      
    
      
      

        1461
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                var h = parseInt(m[1], 10);


      

      
    
      
      

        1462
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                if (m[3]) {


      

      
    
      
      

        1463
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                        h %= 12;


      

      
    
      
      

        1464
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                        if (m[3].toLowerCase().charAt(0) == 'p') {


      

      
    
      
      

        1465
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                                h += 12;


      

      
    
      
      

        1466
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                        }


      

      
    
      
      

        1467
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                }


      

      
    
      
      

        1468
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                return h * 60 + (m[2] ? parseInt(m[2], 10) : 0);


      

      
    
      
      

        1469
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
        }


      

      
    
      
      

        1470

function stackSegs(segs) {


      

      
    
      
      

        1676
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
        var levels = [],


      

      
    
      
      

        1677
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                i, len = segs.length, seg,


      

      
    
      
      

        1678
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                j, collide, k;


      

      
    
      
      

        1679
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
        for (i=0; i<len; i++) {


      

      
    
      
      

        1680
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                seg = segs[i];


      

      
    
      
      

        1681
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                j = 0; // the level index where seg should belong


      

      
    
      
      

        1682
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                while (true) {


      

      
    
      
      

        1683
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                        collide = false;


      

      
    
      
      

        1684
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                        if (levels[j]) {


      

      
    
      
      

        1685
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin

        1686
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                                        if (segsCollide(levels[j][k], seg)) {


      

      
    
      
      

        1687
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                                                collide = true;


      

      
    
      
      

        1688
        
        ea70c3d5

        1689
        
        ea70c3d5

        1690
        
        ea70c3d5

                                }

        1692
        
        ea70c3d5

                        if (collide) {


      

      
    
      
      

        1693
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                                j++;


      

      
    
      
      

        1694
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                        }else{


      

      
    
      
      

        1695
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                                break;


      

      
    
      
      

        1696
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                        }


      

      
    
      
      

        1697
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                }


      

      
    
      
      

        1698
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                if (levels[j]) {


      

      
    
      
      

        1699
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                        levels[j].push(seg);


      

      
    
      
      

        1700
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                }else{


      

      
    
      
      

        1701
        
        ea70c3d5

        1702

        1703
        
        ea70c3d5

        1705
        
        ea70c3d5

function countForwardSegs(levels) {


      

      
    
      
      

        4212
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
        var i, j, k, level, segForward, segBack;


      

      
    
      
      

        4213
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
        for (i=levels.length-1; i>0; i--) {


      

      
    
      
      

        4214
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                level = levels[i];


      

      
    
      
      

        4215
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                for (j=0; j<level.length; j++) {


      

      
    
      
      

        4216
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                        segForward = level[j];


      

      
    
      
      

        4217
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                        for (k=0; k<levels[i-1].length; k++) {


      

      
    
      
      

        4218
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                                segBack = levels[i-1][k];


      

      
    
      
      

        4219
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                                if (segsCollide(segForward, segBack)) {


      

      
    
      
      

        4220
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                                        segBack.forward = Math.max(segBack.forward||0, (segForward.forward||0)+1);


      

      
    
      
      

        4221
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                                }


      

      
    
      
      

        4222
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                        }


      

      
    
      
      

        4223
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
                }


      

      
    
      
      

        4224
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
        }


      

      
    
      
      

        4225
        
        ea70c3d5
        Redmine Admin
        
}
